AssetCacheTetheratorService(8) System Manager's Manual AssetCacheTetheratorService(8)

NAME

AssetCacheTetheratorService — Service to support Internet sharing with USB devices

SYNOPSIS

AssetCacheTetheratorService

DESCRIPTION

AssetCacheTetheratorService supports sharing the computer's Internet connection with USB devices.

There are no configuration options to AssetCacheTetheratorService. Users should not run AssetCacheTetheratorService manually.

DIAGNOSTICS

AssetCacheTetheratorService logs to the os_log(3) subsystem com.apple.AssetCacheServices category Tetherator.

SEE ALSO

System Preferences > Sharing > Content Caching, log(1), AssetCacheTetheratorUtil(8)
